{
  "chapter": 298,
  "chapter_summary": "本章分两条线展开。寇仲循火光追至遭海贼洗劫的俚僚村庄，独力剿灭二十余名假扮海沙帮的黑衣匪徒，从最后一人口中逼问出幕后主使为林士宏。林士宏此举既抢掠俚僚物资，又嫁祸沈法兴，意图挑起宋阀与沈法兴的冲突。寇仲赶到村心时，正遇三大俚帅之一的欧阳倩率部与崔纪秀所率匪众对峙，寇仲当场揭露崔纪秀身份。另一线，徐子陵扮作岳山在成都截住郑石如，试探其阴癸派身份。郑石如坦言自己虽非派中弟子，却因父亲郑汉堂十年前被害而虚与委蛇，暗藏退隐之心。徐子陵约席应三更在大石寺见面，郑石如警告阴癸派四大元老及婠婠均在成都，且席应新创\"紫气天罗\"魔功极为霸道，但徐子陵坚持冒险行事。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两个僚娘相当不错，希望在那边再找到几个类似的货色就够众兄弟快活快活哩！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "给本人纳命来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bei_fu_da_han",
      "text": "想活命就有问有答，否则我把你的卵蛋捏出来，明白吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bei_fu_da_han",
      "text": "你们是那条线上的人，坦白告诉你，我对你们的来龙去脉一清二楚，现在只是试探你的真诚。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bei_fu_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "被俘大汉",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "大爷饶命，我们是海沙帮的人。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bei_fu_da_han",
      "text": "你是不想保留你的卵蛋哩！让我先帮你脱裤子，我只割你的卵蛋，绝不割其他地方。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bei_fu_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "被俘大汉",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "大爷饶命，我确是海沙帮的人。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bei_fu_da_han",
      "text": "还要骗我，你知老子是谁吗？'美人鱼'游秋雁是我亲过嘴的老相好；'胖刺客'尤贵和'闯将'凌志高都给我踢过屁股，海沙帮由上至下都认识我，你还敢乱说一通。最后机会啦！本大爷再没时间浪费在你的卵蛋上。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bei_fu_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "被俘大汉",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "小人说啦！是林爷派我们来的。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bei_fu_da_han",
      "text": "林爷是那个混蛋？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bei_fu_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "被俘大汉",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "是林士宏大爷！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "郑石如留下，其他人给老夫滚。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位请给点面子小弟，嘿！这是小弟的长辈，各位先行一步，小弟稍后会到散花楼与诸位赔罪。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不知前辈法驾光临，请恕石如怠慢之罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "随我来！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "小子你在阴癸派究竟是何级数职份，所授何色。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不瞒前辈，严格来说，石如并非阴癸派的弟子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "废话！如你是外人，祝玉妍怎会信任你？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "其中一言难尽，不过前辈若要我代为传话，绝无问题。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "小子倒相当机伶，你怎知我要你代为传话。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "前辈今次重出江湖，不用说都是冲着宋缺和席应两人而来，前辈这刻突然现身成都，当是收到有关席应的风声，晚辈有说错吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "席应在那里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "前辈该比晚辈更清楚席应的性格，他是绝不会把行踪透露予任何人知道的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "边不负怕是唯一的例外吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这个我不太清楚，前辈可知我乃郑汉堂的儿子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "汉堂仍在生吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "家父在十年前去世，前辈当然明白他老人家为何难得善终。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "汉堂定是想退出啦！对吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "正是如此，否则爹怎会死得那么不明不白！不瞒前辈说，现在小侄只是虚与委蛇，静候时机。这番心底的想法，小侄尚是首趟向人透露，皆因前辈当年曾帮过爹的大忙，小侄实不忍眼看前辈中计饮恨成都，望岳老体谅！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_ji_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "崔纪秀",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_qian",
      "text": "竟是'虎衣红粉'欧阳倩大小姐芳驾光临，区区幸何如之。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_qian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳倩",
      "listener": "char_cui_ji_xiu",
      "text": "给我报上名来？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_cui_ji_xiu",
      "text": "本人崔纪秀，在林士宏座下居国师要职，今趟到这里杀人放火，除因天生凶残成性外，更为要嫁祸沈法兴。哈！崔兄！小弟这番代答有说错吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "席应的手段，怎瞒得过老夫，自听到席应这狗贼的消息，老夫知道别有内情，贤侄不用为老夫担忧，究竟贤侄是否晓得席应落脚的地点？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "岳老万勿等闲视之。他们要对付的不单是宋缺，还有你老人家。如非祝玉妍不愿亲自下手杀死女儿的亲爹，那天岳老怎能这么容易脱身。事后他们曾搜遍洛阳，只是找不着岳老吧！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "当日初遇时，贤侄的说话隐有招揽之意，究竟是甚么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "岳老出现得太突然，直至祝玉妍证实岳老的身份，小侄才肯相信，但已找不到岳老。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "阴癸派一向不许外人参与他们的秘密，为何你能知道这么多事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "换了我是岳老，也会有同样的疑惑。问题是我虽非阴癸派弟子，却非是外人，十年来我一直对家父的横死丝毫不露怀疑，又故意装出迷恋祝玉妍的徒弟白清儿的样子，兼之他们要借助小侄在政治经济的才能，为他们管治襄阳这重要的城寨，所以能得祝玉妍重用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "贤侄今次到成都，所为何事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "此事一言难尽，简单的说，就是我终于找到心头爱，又因父仇无望得报，故生出退隐江湖之心，恰巧遇上席应的事。岳老最好立即远避他方，将来再设法找席应算账。我会如实把岳老现身此处的事报上去，说的当然是另一番话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "贤侄放心，老夫若没有把握，绝不会涉险来此，贤侄甚么都不用理，只须告诉他们今晚三更时份我会在大石寺等待席应便成。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "岳老万不可如此，阴癸派四大元老高手刻下全在成都，尚有祝玉妍的得意弟子婠婠，岳老绝难讨好。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "老夫自有分寸，贤侄你至紧要把老夫的话如实告诉边不负，否则必将误事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "岳老果然练成'换日大法'，难怪如此有自信。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "但岳老必须小心，据说席应集西域诸家大成，创出名为'紫气天罗'的霸道魔功，祝玉妍试招后亦要赞不绝口，推许为石之轩'不死印'外魔门最精采的自创功法。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "快去依计行事，千万勿要误事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 298,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    }
  ],
